<h4>
2.5.4. Setting or Changing Course Grading Scheme</h4>
</a>
<p> To change the grade schema in the program, click the 'Grading' option on the toolbar, and then click 'Grade Schema'. This is illustrated in Figure 1. 
</p>
<p>This is shown below, in Figure 1.
<hr>
<a name="Figure Add Student path">
